{
  "name": "Invisibility",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-blue-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You magically cloak a target within range for the duration. Make a DC 15 Spell Check.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is Invisible.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The target is Invisible and can immediately take the Hide Action for free.</p></li></ul><p>The Spell ends early if the target takes any Action or Reaction beside the Move, Dodge, Hide, or Sustain Actions.</p><p><em><strong>DC Tip:</strong> Being invisible makes you Unseen, but if you want to be fully Hidden from a creature you need to take the Hide action to also become Unheard.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The duration increases by 1 step (1 min → 10 min → 1 hour → 8 hours → Long Rest).</p><p><strong>Mass Invisibility: (1 AP and X MP)</strong> You can target X additional creatures within range.</p><p><strong>Greater Invisibility: (3 MP)</strong> Choose 1 target. The Spell no longer ends early when the target takes any Action or Reaction.</p>",
